flowchart TD
    A[List Companies Request] --> B[Validate JWT Token]
    B --> C{Token Valid?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    C -->|Yes| E[Extract User Role]
    E --> F{Admin Role?}
    F -->|No| G[Return 403 Forbidden]
    F -->|Yes| H[Parse Query Parameters]
    H --> I{Valid Parameters?}
    I -->|No| J[Return 400 Invalid Parameters]
    I -->|Yes| K[Check Cache for Companies List]
    K --> L{Cache Hit?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Retrieve from Cache]
    L -->|No| N[Query Database]
    N --> O[Apply Filters & Pagination]
    O --> P[Apply Company Status Filter]
    P --> Q[Sort Results]
    Q --> R[Cache Results]
    R --> M
    M --> S[Format Response Data]
    S --> T[Return 200 OK with Companies]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style D fill:#ffebee
    style G fill:#ffebee
    style J fill:#ffebee
    style T fill:#e8f5e8